data.label: FAQ Documents
data.payload:
How do I reset my password? Go to Settings > Security > Reset Password and follow the instructions.

How do I contact support? Email us at support@example.com or use the live chat feature in the bottom right corner.

What payment methods do you accept? We accept credit cards, PayPal, and bank transfers for enterprise customers.

How do I upgrade my account? Navigate to Account Settings > Subscription and choose your desired plan.

metadata.name: Knowledge Base Builder
metadata.description: Build a searchable knowledge base by embedding and storing FAQ documents in Qdrant
